description:
Kinoversio de novelo de Boris Polevoj, bazita sur reala historio de piloto Aleksej Maresjev (1916-2001). Kun subtitoloj en Esperanto. Vidu pli detale che http://kinejo.blogsome.com/2007/05/20/novelo-pri-la-vera-homo-1948/

Alexey Meresyev was a fighter pilot during the war. One day he was shot down by Nazis, and because of his wounds both of his legs had to be cut off up to his knees. Because of his spirit and courage, Alexey was able to overcome his disability. He learned not only to walk on his artificial limps, but even dance and fly the plane again. Based on a real-life story. (Plot summary from imdb.com). Internal subtitles in Esperanto.

